      3: { rank: 4, highlight: 'Dark Angel — "The Fastest Band Alive"', reason: 'Gene Hoglan earned his "Atomic Clock" nickname partly through his tenure with Dark Angel, a band billed as "The Fastest Band Alive" that chased speed metal\'s tempo ceiling to its most extreme conclusion in the mid-to-late 1980s' },
