      6: { rank: 1, highlight: 'Evans heads credited directly in his own kit profile', reason: 'George Kollias\'s own MetalForge kit profile credits Evans heads as part of the setup that lets him sustain 240+ BPM blast beats with surgical clarity, running durable, two-ply batter heads able to survive the direct, linear action of his co-designed Pearl Demon XR double pedal night after night. The extra ply resists the head fatigue a single-ply batter would suffer under that kind of sustained abuse, keeping his attack consistent across a full set. Kollias earns rank #1 for the most explicitly documented drumhead brand credit in MetalForge\'s own gear data.' },
